scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: Telegram 1: From Elliott (Dot) to E.R. McClelland at Guignol Theatre, OK Jimmy Stewart Lets See You Win the Academy Award. Telegram 2: From Tracy to Mike at Guignol Theatre, If I Survive Interview Will be Entirely Courtesy Gentleman From Southbend. You're Doing a Swell Job Mike.
